<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7a912f39-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s8935"><num value="8935">§ 8935.</num><heading> Collaboration</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">In carrying out this subchapter, the Director shall collaborate with—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id7a912f3a-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s8935/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> appropriate Federal and State regulators;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id7a912f3b-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s8935/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> institutions of higher education;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id7a912f3c-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s8935/3"><num value="3">(3)</num><content> research institutions; and</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id7a912f3d-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s8935/4"><num value="4">(4)</num><content> other expert stakeholders.</content>
</paragraph>
